law.history: Repealed 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 393, sec. 48, effective July 14, 2000; amended 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 393, sec. 36, effective July 14, 2000. -- Created 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 213, sec. 5, effective July 15, 1998.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Licensed person to notify commissioner of licensure disciplinary action.
metadata.lrc-note: (7/14/00). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 393, sec. 48, prevails over its amendment in 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 393, sec. 36.
